{
  "stem": "25651.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ben Yehuda was undeveloped on the eastern side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My uncle was still alive because I was in Israel in 1948.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says she said, all this sand, who wants to buy all this sand?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think we'll back now to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, she didn't buy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was-- she didn't obey her father-- her-- her husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't sign the contract.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's more, the one parcel that she was obligated to give to the [INAUDIBLE] family, because she took a third of the house to give to Lea, the other aunt, you see, as a dowry-- she gave them the money and she advised her in-law, Zeev Charif, buy yourself a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Michael, my cousin, says, you would have been millionaires if your mother had done what your father said.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we would have been millionaires if we had just bought that one parcel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we made a lot of money because we bought a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he bought a [INAUDIBLE] in the countryside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this was an error.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wonder-- I keep thinking, when I was saying goodbye to her, the tragedy sort of was at her feet, you know, that she had brought three sons into captivity.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So her meddling or muddling, and so not obeying, so following her own mind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she was just wrong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it's no fault of hers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when I was 16, I was still bitter about the fault of hers, the-- the-- the tremendous error, you know, of judgment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But to me, this is a moment that I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I remember this tragic error that we were there but for the chance of my aunt committing suicide, and my uncle writing to her, come and buy, and denying to her that her sister was-- had committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
